text: Hanna Motrechko (; born 14 May 1965) is a Soviet rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Unified Team Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
